  "text": "Cytosolic Trx h3 and Trx h5 are essential to promote monomerization of NPR1, and the expression of Trx h5 is associated with senescence [CITATION_1] . To test whether the activation of NPR1 by MPK6 involves redox regulation, the expression and activation of Trx h was measured in both WT and mpk6-3 mutant plants.",
